<%  end_time = Time.now
    begin_time = 1.day.ago(end_time)
    users = DailyReports.successful_user_logins(begin_time, end_time)  -%>
Successful Logins:
All times are in UTC timezone
	Starting Time: <%= begin_time %>
	Ending   Time: <%= end_time %>
Name      Number of Logins      Logins Per Day        Roles
-----------------------------------------------------------
<% users.each do |user| -%> <%= user.name %>      <%= user[:logins]%>      <%= (user[:logins] / ((end_time - begin_time) / (60 * 60 * 24))).round(2) %>      <%= user.main_role -%> <% end -%>